                            },
                            "elements": [
                                {
                                    "id": "2456d4dd",
                                    "settings": {
                                        "title": "1. Start with a thermal base layer\n",
                                        "header_size": "h4"
                                    },
                                    "widgetType": "heading",
                                    "elType": "widget"
                                },
                                {
                                    "id": "500b8fdc",
                                    "settings": {
                                        "editor": "<p>Merino wool or silk long-sleeves trap heat while wicking moisture away. Avoid cotton as it stays wet and makes you colder.</p>",
                                        "__globals__": {
                                            "text_color": "globals/colors?id=65246f0"
                                        }
                                    },
                                    "widgetType": "text-editor",
                                    "elType": "widget"
                                }
                            ],
                            "elType": "container",
                            "isInner": true
                        },
                        {
                            "id": "1d578f67",
                            "settings": {
                                "content_width": "full",
                                "flex_gap": {
                                    "column": "0",
                                    "row": "20",
                                    "isLinked": false,
                                    "unit": "px",
                                    "size": 0
                                },
                                "ma_el_slider_delay": "5000",
                                "_title": "Content"
                            },
                            "elements": [
                                {
                                    "id": "66886381",
                                    "settings": {
                                        "title": "2. Insulate with fleece or down mid-layers\n",
                                        "header_size": "h4"
                                    },
                                    "widgetType": "heading",
                                    "elType": "widget"
                                },
                                {
                                    "id": "1247eb23",
                                    "settings": {
                                        "editor": "<p>A lightweight puffy jacket or fleece pullover adds core warmth without bulk. Perfect under a shell coat.</p>",
                                        "__globals__": {
                                            "text_color": "globals/colors?id=65246f0"
                                        }
                                    },
                                    "widgetType": "text-editor",
                                    "elType": "widget"
                                }
                            ],
                            "elType": "container",
                            "isInner": true
                        },
                        {
                            "id": "7bf2194c",
                            "settings": {
                                "content_width": "full",
                                "flex_gap": {
                                    "column": "0",
                                    "row": "20",
                                    "isLinked": false,
                                    "unit": "px",
                                    "size": 0
                                },
                                "ma_el_slider_delay": "5000",
                                "_title": "Content"
                            },
                            "elements": [
                                {
                                    "id": "5912d29a",
                                    "settings": {
                                        "title": "3. Choose a wind & water-resistant outer shell",
                                        "header_size": "h4"
                                    },
                                    "widgetType": "heading",
                                    "elType": "widget"
                                },
                                {
                                    "id": "6bb98fb6",
                                    "settings": {
                                        "editor": "<p>Your jacket should block wind and repel snow/rain. Look for taped seams and adjustable cuffs.</p>",
                                        "__globals__": {
                                            "text_color": "globals/colors?id=65246f0"
                                        }
                                    },
                                    "widgetType": "text-editor",
                                    "elType": "widget"
                                }
                            ],
                            "elType": "container",
                            "isInner": true
                        },
                        {
                            "id": "d78611d",
                            "settings": {
                                "content_width": "full",
                                "flex_gap": {
                                    "column": "0",
                                    "row": "20",
                                    "isLinked": false,
                                    "unit": "px",
                                    "size": 0
                                },
                                "ma_el_slider_delay": "5000",
                                "_title": "Content"
                            },
                            "elements": [
                                {
                                    "id": "1227dcfd",
                                    "settings": {
                                        "title": "4. Wool coats over synthetic blends\n",
                                        "header_size": "h4"
                                    },
                                    "widgetType": "heading",
                                    "elType": "widget"
                                },
                                {
                                    "id": "1ce0c3e9",
                                    "settings": {
                                        "editor": "<p>For city winters, a 70\u201380% wool coat offers timeless elegance and natural insulation.</p>",
                                        "__globals__": {
                                            "text_color": "globals/colors?id=65246f0"
                                        }
                                    },
                                    "widgetType": "text-editor",
                                    "elType": "widget"
                                }
                            ],
                            "elType": "container",
                            "isInner": true
                        },
                        {
                            "id": "1dbd353b",
                            "settings": {
                                "content_width": "full",
                                "flex_gap": {
                                    "column": "0",
                                    "row": "20",
                                    "isLinked": false,
                                    "unit": "px",
                                    "size": 0
                                },
                                "ma_el_slider_delay": "5000",
                                "_title": "Content"
                            },
                            "elements": [
                                {
                                    "id": "5ad4322",
                                    "settings": {
                                        "title": "5. Don't forget your neck and head",
                                        "header_size": "h4"
                                    },
                                    "widgetType": "heading",
                                    "elType": "widget"
                                },
                                {
                                    "id": "7f35faa3",
                                    "settings": {
                                        "editor": "<p>Up to 30% of body heat escapes from the head and neck. A cashmere beanie and a merino scarf make a huge difference.</p>",
                                        "__globals__": {
                                            "text_color": "globals/colors?id=65246f0"
                                        }
                                    },
                                    "widgetType": "text-editor",
                                    "elType": "widget"
                                }
                            ],
                            "elType": "container",
                            "isInner": true
                        },
                        {
                            "id": "5c5ddbb4",
                            "settings": {
                                "content_width": "full",
                                "flex_gap": {
                                    "column": "0",
                                    "row": "20",
                                    "isLinked": false,
                                    "unit": "px",
                                    "size": 0
                                },
                                "ma_el_slider_delay": "5000",
                                "_title": "Content"
                            },
                            "elements": [
                                {
                                    "id": "d7a8621",
                                    "settings": {
                                        "title": "6. Layer your gloves",
                                        "header_size": "h4"
                                    },
                                    "widgetType": "heading",
                                    "elType": "widget"
                                },
                                {
                                    "id": "5399edbb",
                                    "settings": {
                                        "editor": "<p>Thin liner gloves + insulated leather/ski gloves keep fingers flexible and warm.</p>",
                                        "__globals__": {
                                            "text_color": "globals/colors?id=65246f0"
                                        }
                                    },
                                    "widgetType": "text-editor",
                                    "elType": "widget"
                                }
                            ],
                            "elType": "container",
                            "isInner": true
                        },
                        {
                            "id": "51142fdd",
                            "settings": {
                                "content_width": "full",
                                "flex_gap": {
                                    "column": "0",
                                    "row": "20",
                                    "isLinked": false,
                                    "unit": "px",
                                    "size": 0
                                },
                                "ma_el_slider_delay": "5000",
                                "_title": "Content"
                            },
                            "elements": [
                                {
                                    "id": "56603214",
                                    "settings": {
                                        "title": "7. Wool socks are non-negotiable",
                                        "header_size": "h4"
                                    },
                                    "widgetType": "heading",
                                    "elType": "widget"
                                },
                                {
                                    "id": "1a04424d",
                                    "settings": {
                                        "editor": "<p>Cotton socks in winter boots = cold feet. Choose merino wool socks (hiking or dress weight).</p>",
                                        "__globals__": {
                                            "text_color": "globals/colors?id=65246f0"
                                        }
                                    },
                                    "widgetType": "text-editor",
                                    "elType": "widget"
                                }
                            ],
                            "elType": "container",
                            "isInner": true
                        },
                        {
                            "id": "72694a68",
                            "settings": {
                                "content_width": "full",
                                "flex_gap": {
                                    "column": "0",
                                    "row": "20",
                                    "isLinked": false,
                                    "unit": "px",
                                    "size": 0
                                },
                                "ma_el_slider_delay": "5000",
                                "_title": "Content"
                            },
                            "elements": [
                                {
                                    "id": "37cc8983",
                                    "settings": {
                                        "title": "8. Insulated, waterproof boots",
                                        "header_size": "h4"
                                    },
                                    "widgetType": "heading",
                                    "elType": "widget"
                                },
                                {
                                    "id": "59f26e83",
                                    "settings": {
                                        "editor": "<p>Look for boots with thermal rating (e.g., Thinsulate or shearling lining) and deep tread for ice.</p>",
                                        "__globals__": {
                                            "text_color": "globals/colors?id=65246f0"
                                        }
                                    },
                                    "widgetType": "text-editor",
                                    "elType": "widget"
                                }
                            ],
                            "elType": "container",
                            "isInner": true
                        },
                        {
                            "id": "2944d62c",
                            "settings": {
                                "content_width": "full",
                                "flex_gap": {
                                    "column": "0",
                                    "row": "20",
                                    "isLinked": false,
                                    "unit": "px",
                                    "size": 0
                                },
                                "ma_el_slider_delay": "5000",
                                "_title": "Content"
                            },
                            "elements": [
                                {
                                    "id": "11b66c97",
                                    "settings": {
                                        "title": "9. Play with textures and proportions",
                                        "header_size": "h4"
                                    },
                                    "widgetType": "heading",
                                    "elType": "widget"
                                },
                                {
                                    "id": "4c146891",
                                    "settings": {
                                        "editor": "<p>Chunky knits with slim pants, or an oversized scarf with a tailored coat \u2014 winter is perfect for layered silhouettes.</p>",
                                        "__globals__": {
                                            "text_color": "globals/colors?id=65246f0"
                                        }
                                    },
                                    "widgetType": "text-editor",
                                    "elType": "widget"
                                }
                            ],
                            "elType": "container",
                            "isInner": true
                        },
                        {
                            "id": "3e319494",
                            "settings": {
                                "content_width": "full",
                                "flex_gap": {
                                    "column": "0",
                                    "row": "20",
                                    "isLinked": false,
                                    "unit": "px",
                                    "size": 0
                                },
                                "ma_el_slider_delay": "5000",
                                "_title": "Content"
                            },
                            "elements": [
                                {
                                    "id": "364a9ddb",
                                    "settings": {
                                        "title": "10. Accessorize smartly",
                                        "header_size": "h4"
                                    },
                                    "widgetType": "heading",
                                    "elType": "widget"
                                },
                                {
                                    "id": "23751b7f",
                                    "settings": {
                                        "editor": "<p>Leather gloves, a bold beanie, or a structured tote can elevate even the coziest outfit.</p><p>Remember: Winter style is not about suffering \u2014 it's about strategic layering and investing in quality fabrics. Stay warm and stylish!</p>",
                                        "column_gap": {
                                            "unit": "px",
                                            "size": 0,
                                            "sizes": []
                                        },
                                        "paragraph_spacing": {
                                            "unit": "px",
